Effective Date: February 10, 2024

At Tally Golf Scores, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect from users, how we use it, and how we safeguard your data. By using the Tally Golf Scores mobile application, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.

Information we collect

We collect the following information when you use the Tally Golf Scores app:

Personal Information: 

-	We collect your name, email address, and gender.
-	Golf Round Data: We collect data regarding the golf rounds you enter, including your scores for each hole.

How We Use Your Information
                        
We use the information we collect for the following purposes:
-	To provide and enhance the functionality of the app, including tracking and displaying golf scores.
-	To communicate with you regarding your account or updates to the app.

Data Sharing and Disclosure

We do not share your personal information with third parties, except where required by law. Your data is not sold, traded, or otherwise shared with external organizations.

Children's Privacy

Tally Golf Scores is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone under 13 years of age. If we become aware that a child under 13 has provided us with personal information, we will take steps to delete such information from our records.
If you believe that we may have collected information from a child under 13, please contact us at support@tallygolfscores.com so we can promptly address the issue.     

Location Information or Analytics

We do not collect any location-based data or analytics regarding how you access or use our system. Your activity within the app is not tracked for analysis or marketing purposes.
Data Deletion
You have the right to request the deletion of your personal data. If you wish to delete your account or personal information, please contact us at:
support@tallygolfscores.com
                   
Security

We take reasonable precautions to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of data transmission or storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any significant changes by updating the effective date at the top of this policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, or if you would like to request data deletion, please contact us at: support@tallygolfscores.com
By using the Tally Golf Scores app, you consent to the collection and use of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.
